            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Coat your <strong>basa fillet[s]</strong> in the <strong>flour</strong>, tap off any excess, then add to the <strong>beaten egg</strong> and finally press it into your <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong> firmly to coat everything evenly – this is your <strong>breaded basa</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
