        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> (enough to coat the base of the pan) over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> breaded basa </strong>and cook for 4-5 min on each side, or until golden and cooked through</p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked when it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
