      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top the <strong>toasted ciabatta half</strong> with the<strong> lettuce leaves</strong>, a dollop of <strong>remoulade</strong> and the <strong>breaded basa </strong>– this is your<strong> open Scandi-style basa sandwich</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>open Scandi-style basa sandwich </strong>with the <strong>chips</strong> and any <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>remoulade </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
